Garbanguly's Gauntlet

Each player starts the round by coming up with a trivia question. The trivia topic is up to each individual player. The topic may be
anything so long as it is possible for each player to reasonably answer the question. The players then take turns answering the
trivia questions. For each question a player gets correct, 1 point is awarded. The first player to answer 5 questions correctly wins,
and gets 1 JORKLE! Every time a player answers incorrectly they must take 1 drink.

Everytime a player says the word "Garbanguly" each player must take a knee, last player to take a knee must take a drink.